original_title: Tammy Wynette and Country Sisters: Legends In Concert
overview: Tammy Wynette is joined in this fabulous performance with eight of her lovely singing sisters, with twenty one tracks of pure country pleasure. Tammy's line-up of country sisters includes Gail Davies with a number of her top hits and Lyn Paul with number one hit 'Stand By Your Man.' Tammy also plays some of her number one hits such as "Till I Can Make It On My Own' and 'Womanhood' in this unforgettable hour long show.
tagline: Tammy Wynette and Country Sisters: Legends In Concert
title: Tammy Wynette and Country Sisters: Legends In Concert
